posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID #247029', 'Lease today and receive up to 8 weeks free!', 'Welcome - where elegant residences meet unparalleled amenities within the vibrant Regent Square district at the heart of Houston.', 'Experience an elevated way of life, with world-class restaurant and retail anchored by James Beard award-winning chefs and lush tree-lined sidewalks and lawns.', 'Designed to endlessly inspire, exhilarate, and motivate, The Sterling welcomes you to experience a comprehensive lifestyle embodying the best of cosmopolitan living.', 'Live, play and celebrate outdoors in our covered terrace The Piazza.', " Enjoy ceiling hung cabana seating, five 70 inch TV's, ping pong, corn hole, a stunning feature island, and a feature stone-clad fireplace - all fully covered.", 'Work meets play in our media lounge.', 'En-suite conference rooms let you customize your workday and collaborate.', " Play Billiards, watch one of our two 70 inch TV's or enjoy a beverage at our full bar-all while surrounded by stunning sculptures, art and a stone waterfall-sided island.", 'Bike Storage', 'Concierge Services', 'CoWorking Area', 'Dry Cleaning/Laundry Service', 'Electric Car Charging', 'Fiber Optic Lines', 'Locker System', 'Outdoor Kitchen', 'Pet Washing Station', 'Recycling', 'Smoke Free', 'Wifi Access', 'Billiard Room', 'Club House', 'Dog/Walk Trail', 'Spa/Jacuzzi']
